::Razor::

Once again the Transwarp portal opens as a very odd looking craft comes through it, and heads at full speed towards Earth. It appears to be a Earth style F-14 fighter jet, however it has atmospheric armor and interplanetary propulsion units. The craft enters into Earth&#39;s atmosphere and continues on it&#39;s way. The armor and propulsion part break away and fall to Earth. The jet&#39;s true design is seen.(Think of when Wing Gundam first comes to Earth in the first episode of MS Gundam Wing)

The jet comes down where the parts had fallen, located just outside a cave in what would become Hollywood, California.

The jet transformes to reveal slick black and silver Decepticon Seeker.

&quot;So this is Earth. Finally no prisons to keep me locked up in. Cybertron&#39;s regulations on this planet are too strict to send a team after me. I will finally be able to build my army,&quot; Razor goes on to himself.

He gathers up the fallen parts and takes them into the cave. He starts to construct a massive computer system from the parts.

